_sText:
Designed and mapped by Zilly & Steezy

Notes

A jailbreak map textured with christmas and minecraft from top to bottom.

Map features

  • Random gun cell
  • Multiple vents around the map
  • Multiple guns around the map
  • Easy access to all the games with fun rebel opportunities
  • Different Minecraft themed areas (cave, desert & snow)

Activities

  • TNT course
  • Sword arena
  • Dodge the minecart
  • Spleef (with guns)
  • Race
  • Ice race
  • Bunny hop
  • Talent room
  • Colours
  • Breakfloor
  • Couch game
  • Climb
  • Football
